notes.title: Data Availability
notes.p: The data cannot be shared publicly due to ethical consideration surrounding this qualitative research. Specifically, interview transcripts may contain potential identifiable information and selected participants could be potentially identified via the context of the provided data. However, we will make these data available upon request for interested researchers. Such requests can be made by contacting Allison Gottwalt ( allison_gottwalt@med.unc.edu).
